{"descriptions":[{"authors":[{"fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre","id":"6"}],"source_url":null,"content":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">Connectives (coordinating and subordinating conjunctions) constitute a category in Literary Tibetan in which there are major divergences from the spoken language. The following table lists some of these differences</p> <table style=\"width: 607px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"223\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><strong>Literary</strong></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><strong>Standard Spoken</strong></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"223\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཅིང་</span> / Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྟེ་</span> / Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་དང་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;&ldquo;And&rdquo;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"223\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པས་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཙང་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;Because,&rdquo; &ldquo;As,&rdquo; &ldquo;Since&rdquo;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"223\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པར་བརྟེན་</span> / Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྟབས་</span> / Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཤིས་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཙང་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;Because,&rdquo; &ldquo;As,&rdquo; &ldquo;Since&rdquo;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"223\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཕྱིར་དུ་</span> / Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སླད་དུ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཡག་ལ་</span> (*L)</p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To,&rdquo; &ldquo;In order to&rdquo;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"223\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པས་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ནས་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;Then,&rdquo; &ldquo;And,&rdquo; &ldquo;After&rdquo;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"223\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་དང་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་ད་ག་</span> (*L)</p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;As soon as&rdquo;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"223\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པའི་ཚེ་</span> / Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པའི་ན་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པའི་སྐབས་ལ་</span> / Verb + <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དུས་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;When&rdquo;</p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table>","created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:49 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:49 UTC","id":1397,"title":null,"is_primary":true}]}